{{vgname|小人闖天下|en=The Pedestrian|cn=步行者|tw=小人闖天下}}是美國工作室Skookum Arts開發並發行的[[橫向捲軸遊戲|橫向捲軸]]型[[益智遊戲|益智遊戲]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/359921/How_Skookum_Arts_built_The_Pedestrian_puzzles_out_of_urban_signage.php|title=How Skookum Arts built The Pedestrian puzzles out of urban signage|website=Gamasutra|accessdate=August 6, 2020|archive-date=2020-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200323151347/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/359921/How_Skookum_Arts_built_The_Pedestrian_puzzles_out_of_urban_signage.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。遊戲於2020年1月首發，對應[[Linux|Linux]]、[[macOS|macOS]]和[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]平台。[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]和[[PlayStation_5|PlayStation 5]]移植版於2021年1月發行；[[任天堂Switch|任天堂Switch]]、[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]和[[Xbox_Series_X/S|Xbox Series X/S]]移植版發行時間待定<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gematsu.com/2021/01/the-pedestrian-coming-to-ps5-and-ps4-on-january-29-xbox-series-xbox-one-and-switch-later|title=The Pedestrian coming to PS5 and PS4 on January 29; Xbox Series, Xbox One, and Switch later|website=Gematsu|last=Romano|first=Sal|date=January 18, 2021|access-date=January 18, 2021|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121041939/https://www.gematsu.com/2021/01/the-pedestrian-coming-to-ps5-and-ps4-on-january-29-xbox-series-xbox-one-and-switch-later|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

